### Mutiple Owners of Mutable Data by Combining `Rc<T>` & `RefCell<T>`

- Recall
    - `Rc<T>`: Multiple owner of immutable access data
    - `Rc<RefCell<T>>`: Multiple owners and can mutate that data

```rust
